ight:210px;">            	<img src="images/shafts-4.gif" width="132" height="184" alt="Shafts" class="photo" />                <p>Schaffner can build a buff stack to meet your specifications for shaft type, buff diameter, buff width and spacing. All Schaffner stack buffs are balanced and stacks compressed.</p>				<p>If you would like more information about Schaffner Stack Buffs, call us at 412-716-9902 or use one of the links below to contact us.</p>            </div>        </div><!--col-left-->                <div class="col-right">        <?php include_once ('includes/r-engineer.php'); ?>        <?php include_once ('includes/hp-right.php'); ?>	        </div><!--col-right--><?php include_once ('includes/footer.php'); ?>        